'''Yorodani Riber''' ni umukinnyi wa filimi kubijyanye no kuziyobora no kuzitunganya muri [[Zimbabwe]] yavukiye [[Tanzaniya]] ,kandi akora nka Screenwriter, Producer, Editor na Sound engineer . <ref name="Bio">https://www.paff.org/films/#!/film/fatuma</ref>

== Ubuzima n'uburere ==
Riber yavukiye mu muryango w'umuhungu John na Louise Riber, bombi niba ari abakora amafilime, akurira i [[Harare]], muri [[Zimbabwe]] . Igihe kinini yamaranye muma firime no mubikoresho byo kubyara nyuma yo gukura. Yarangije mu 2004 muri Fairhaven College, Western Washington University, Bellingham, Washington, [[Leta Zunze Ubumwe z’Amerika|Amerika]], aho yize Filime. <ref>https://alumni.wwu.edu/out-africa</ref> Kuva mu 2005, yari umukinnyi wa firime ukora umwuga wa injeniyeri na injeniyeri y'amajwi i Dar es Salaam, muri [[Tanzaniya]] . 

== Umwuga ==
Mu mwaka wa 2012, yayoboye kandi ahindura ''Siri ya Mtungi'', ikiganiro cya televiziyo [[Igiswahili|y’ururimi]] rwigiswahiri cyamasaha nigice, yakinnye na Cathryn Credo, Beatrice Taisamo, Yvonne Cherrie nabandi. <ref>https://www.worldcat.org/title/siri-ya-mtungi/oclc/1019443274</ref> Yatorewe ibihembo bya "Televiziyo Nziza - Urwenya / Ikinamico", "Filime Yururimi Kavukire / Urukurikirane rw'igiswahili" hamwe na "Best Sound Editor" mu bihembo bya Afurika Magic Viewers Choice Awards 2014 (AMVCA). <ref>https://www.gistmania.com/talk/topic,183819.msg3875713.html</ref>

Muri 2017, yayoboye film, ''Hadithi za Kumekucha: Tunu'' . <ref>https://africanstudies.stanford.edu/events/sgs-summer-film-festival-hadithi-za-kumekucha-tunu</ref>

Muri 2018, yayoboye, atunganya kandi ahindura filime ye ya kabiri yerekana, ''Hadithi za Kumekucha: Fatuma'', yakinnye kandi na Cathryn Credo, Beatrice Taisamo na Ayoub Bombwe .  <ref>https://m.chicagoreader.com/chicago/fatuma/Film?oid=72063130</ref> Muri uwo mwaka, yayoboye kandi akora ''Bahasha (Ibahasha)'', filime yikinamico, irimo Ayoub Bombwe, Godliver Gordian, Omary Mrisho na Cathryn Credo. <ref>https://m.imdb.com/title/tt8540608/</ref> <ref>https://torontoblackfilm.com/movie/bahasha/</ref> <ref>https://multichoicetalentfactory.com/user/15619</ref>

Mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Zanzibar 2018 (ZIFF) ryatoranijwe ku mugaragaro, ''Bahasha ya Riber niyo filime yatangije'' yerekanwe bwa mbere, hamwe na ''Fatuma'' bashyizwe mu cyiciro cya "Long Feature". <ref>http://www.ziff.or.tz/selection2018/</ref> Muri ibyo bihembo, yabonye ''Umuyobozi'' ''mwiza na Cinematografiya nziza'', mu cyiciro cyihariye cya Sinema. <ref>https://www.africaleadftf.org/2018/08/27/usaid-tanzania-supported-film-kumekucha-fatuma-wins-top-swahili-awards-at-2018-zanzibar-film-festival/</ref>

